# Brewfile.air — Air-specific brew/cask additions.
#
# Installed AFTER the shared `Brewfile` on the M3 Air. Use for casks /
# formulae that only the Air needs (e.g. Sidecar-related apps that
# pair with iPad on the road).
#
# To dry-run the Pro's overlay locally:
#   dotctl sync --only=brew --host=pro
